      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you today. It\u2019s a great, honest car that\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
