    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for purchase is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and refreshed throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the high-tension internals. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing versatile damping rates, while power is delivered via an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal traction through corner exit. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with its mileage, the internal mechanical vitals and powertrain response remain sharp and within factory tolerances. A pure, analog driving experience for the discerning petrolhead.",
      "price": 34500.0,
